old routines (checkpoint36 and before) in "diags" are
no longer supported ; To find the equivalent new-version routine, see 
the following list (or example in pkg/timeave, kpg/gmredi or model/src)
------------------------------------------------------------
  pkg/timeave        -|-  diags/inc & diags/src
 
TIMEAVE_STATV.h      <--  AVER.h

timeave_statvars.F   <--  do_time_averages.F
timeave_statv_write.F <--  write_time_averages.F
timeave_reset_1k.F  <--  timeaver_ini_xyz.F
timeave_cumul_1k.F  <--  timeaver_1fld_xyz.F
timeave_norma_1k.F  <--  timeaver_final_xyz.F
timeave_reset.F     <--  timeaver_ini_xy.F
timeave_cumul_2v.F  <--  Nr x timeaver_2fld_xyz.F
timeave_cumulate.F  <--  Nr x timeaver_1fld_xyz.F
timeave_normaliz.F  <--  timeaver_final_xy.F
